OL,3,C75% of UK businesses did nothing to
OL,4,Csupport charities last year, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThree quarters of British businesses
OL,8,Fdid nothing to support charities last
OL,9,Fyear, according to an annual report.
OL,11,FThe Charities Aid Foundation (CAF),
OL,12,Fwhich helps people or organisations
OL,13,Fgive more effectively to charitable
OL,14,Fcauses, said just 25% of UK firms
OL,15,Fdonated to charities in the form of
OL,16,Ftime, cash or goods last year.
