OL,3,C75% of UK businesses did nothing to
OL,4,Csupport charities last year, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe CAF says firms should commit to
OL,8,Fdonating at least 1% of pre-tax
OL,9,Fprofits each year as best practice,
OL,10,Fand that charities would receive
OL,11,Falmost #5 billion in additional
OL,12,Ffunding if they did so.
OL,14,FIn its annual Corporate Giving report
OL,15,Freleased on Thursday, the organisation
OL,16,Fsaid British businesses donated an
OL,17,Festimated #4.2 billion in 2024, with
OL,18,Fnearly half donated by FTSE 100
OL,19,Fcompanies.
