OL,3,C75% of UK businesses did nothing to
OL,4,Csupport charities last year, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThis marked a similar amount donated
OL,8,Fthe year before in 2023, according to
OL,9,Fthe research.
OL,11,FBut this year's report found that only
OL,12,F24 of the FTSE 100 gave at least 1% of
OL,13,Ftheir pre-tax profits to charity last
OL,14,Fyear, down from 28 in the previous
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FIt also found a decline in the amount
OL,18,Fof cash donations given by firms, with
OL,19,Fan estimated #300 million less given
OL,20,Faway last year compared to 2023.
