OL,3,C75% of UK businesses did nothing to
OL,4,Csupport charities last year, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThis was somewhat offset by a rise in
OL,8,Fdonations of goods ` such as medical
OL,9,Fequipment or food ` by an estimated
OL,10,Fvalue of #180 million last year.
OL,12,FWhile in-kind donations are a crucial
OL,13,Fcomponent of corporate charitable
OL,14,Fgiving, cash allows charities to run
OL,15,Feffectively, grow and innovate, CAF
OL,16,Fsaid, as it highlighted the need for
OL,17,Fcompanies to understand the value of
OL,18,Fcash to charity development and to
OL,19,Fstrike the right balance across
OL,20,Fdifferent forms of giving.
