OL,3,C75% of UK businesses did nothing to
OL,4,Csupport charities last year, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FNeil Heslop, CAF chief executive,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Corporate giving is not an
OL,9,Foptional extra.
OL,11,F"It is a cornerstone of responsible
OL,12,Fbusiness that employees and customers
OL,13,Fexpect.
OL,15,F"Yet, at a time when charities
OL,16,Fcontinue to face severe funding
OL,17,Fchallenges, our research reveals that
OL,18,Fmost British businesses are disengaged
OL,19,Ffrom meaningful community investment.
