OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Across the country, there are great
OL,8,Fexamples of businesses working hand-in-
OL,9,Fhand with charities in local areas,
OL,10,Fand demonstrating that sustained,
OL,11,Fpurposeful giving is certainly
OL,12,Fachievable."
OL,14,FThe CAF is also calling for the
OL,15,FGovernment to reintroduce requirements
OL,16,Ffor companies to publicly share their
OL,17,Fcorporate giving as a way to improve
OL,18,Ftransparency and motivate firms to
OL,19,Fsupport causes.
