OL,7,FMr Heslop said ministers have "a
OL,8,Fcrucial role to play in fostering a
OL,9,Frenewed culture of giving and
OL,10,Fencouraging community investment from
OL,11,Fbusinesses to the places and
OL,12,Fcommunities they are a part of".
OL,14,FElsewhere, the CAF said if donations
OL,15,Fhad kept up with inflation, charities
OL,16,Fwould have received #185 million more
OL,17,Fin 2024.
OL,19,FRegionally, businesses in the North
OL,20,FEast of England are the most likely to
OL,21,Fdonate at 41%.
